<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>StreamFlow - Dark Pattern Demo</title>

<style>
body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
  background: #000;
  color: white;
}

/* Navbar */
.nav {
  padding: 15px 40px;
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.85);
  position: fixed;
  width: 100%;
}

.logo {
  color: red;
  font-size: 26px;
  font-weight: bold;
}

/* Hero */
.hero {
  height: 100vh;
  background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1524985069026-dd778a71c7b4') center/cover no-repeat;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 60px;
}

.overlay {
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.65);
  padding: 40px;
  border-radius: 12px;
}

/* Buttons */
.btn {
  padding: 12px 20px;
  margin-top: 15px;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 6px;
  cursor: pointer;
}

.btn-primary {
  background: red;
  color: white;
}

.btn-secondary {
  background: transparent;
  color: #bbb;
  text-decoration: underline;
}

/* Sections */
.section {
  padding: 60px 40px;
}

.cards {
  display: flex;
  gap: 20px;
  margin-top: 20px;
}

.card {
  width: 200px;
  height: 120px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  overflow: hidden;
  position: relative;
}

.card img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
}

.locked {
  position: absolute;
  top: 5px;
  right: 5px;
  background: orange;
  padding: 5px;
  font-size: 12px;
}

/* Panel */
.panel {
  background: #111;
  padding: 20px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  margin-top: 20px;
}

/* Steps */
.step {
  background: #1a1a1a;
  padding: 15px;
  margin-top: 10px;
  border-left: 4px solid red;
  cursor: pointer;
}

.warning {
  color: #ff6b6b;
  margin-top: 10px;
}

.solution {
  background: #0f5132;
  padding: 15px;
  margin-top: 20px;
  border-radius: 10px;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="nav">
  <div class="logo">StreamFlow</div>
</div>

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="overlay">
    <h1>Easy to Join. Hard to Leave.</h1>
    <p>Roach Motel Dark Pattern Demo</p>
    <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="show(2)">Start Free Trial</button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- SECTION 2 -->
<div id="screen2" class="section" style="display:none;">
  <h2>ROACH MOTEL</h2>

  <p>The Roach Motel dark pattern makes it easy to get into a service, but hard to get out.</p>

  <div class="cards">
    <div class="card">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517602302552-471fe67acf66">
      <div class="locked">Locked</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1505685296765-3a2736de412f">
      <div class="locked">Locked</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1497032628192-86f99bcd76bc">
      <div class="locked">Locked</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="panel">
    <h3>How they trap users</h3>
    <p>A subscription service that is easy to sign up for but requires multiple steps or hides cancellation.</p>
    <p><b>Psychological Tactic:</b> Users feel trapped.</p>
    <p><b>Impact:</b></p>
    <ul>
      <li>Forget to cancel</li>
      <li>Unwanted charges</li>
    </ul>
    <p><b>Solution:</b> Make cancellation easy.</p>
  </div>

  <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="show(3)">Continue</button>
</div>

<!-- SECTION 3 -->
<div id="screen3" class="section" style="display:none;">
  <h2>Cancellation Maze</h2>

  <div class="step" onclick="openPopup()">Step 1: Verify account</div>
  <div class="step" onclick="openOffer()">Step 2: Discount offer</div>
  <div class="step" onclick="openFinal()">Step 3: Final confirmation</div>

  <p class="warning">Are you sure you want to lose premium benefits?</p>

  <div class="solution">
    Solution: cancellation should be as easy as sign-up.
  </div>
</div>

<!-- POPUP 1 -->
<div id="popup" style="display:none; position:fixed; width:100%; height:100%; background:rgba(0,0,0,0.8); justify-content:center; align-items:center;">
  <div style="background:#111; padding:20px; border-radius:10px;">
    <h3>Verify Email</h3>
    <input id="emailInput" placeholder="Enter email">
    <button onclick="submitEmail()">Verify</button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- POPUP 2 -->
<div id="offerPopup" style="display:none; position:fixed; width:100%; height:100%; background:rgba(0,0,0,0.8); justify-content:center; align-items:center;">
  <div style="background:#111; padding:20px; border-radius:10px;">
    <h3>50% OFF Offer</h3>
    <button onclick="stay()">Stay</button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- POPUP 3 -->
<div id="finalPopup" style="display:none; position:fixed; width:100%; height:100%; background:rgba(0,0,0,0.8); justify-content:center; align-items:center;">
  <div style="background:#111; padding:20px; border-radius:10px;">
    <h3>😢 We’ll miss you</h3>
    <button onclick="cancel()">Cancel Anyway</button>
  </div>
</div>

<script>
function show(num){
  document.querySelector(".hero").style.display="none";
  document.getElementById("screen2").style.display="none";
  document.getElementById("screen3").style.display="none";
  document.getElementById("screen"+num).style.display="block";
}

function openPopup(){ document.getElementById("popup").style.display="flex"; }
function openOffer(){ document.getElementById("offerPopup").style.display="flex"; }
function openFinal(){ document.getElementById("finalPopup").style.display="flex"; }

function submitEmail(){ alert("Verification sent"); }
function stay(){ alert("Stayed subscribed"); }
function cancel(){ alert("Cancelled"); }
</script>

</body>
</html>
